title: 1923 Akron Pros season
text: The <a href="1923%20NFL%20season">1923</a> <a href="Akron%20Pros">Akron Pros</a> season was their fourth in the <a href="National%20Football%20League">league</a>. The team failed to improve on their <a href="1922%20Akron%20Pros%20season">previous output</a> of 3–5–2, winning only one game. They tied for sixteenth place in the league.
